        <h4>INFORMATIZATION SERVICES GENERAL COORDINATION</h4>
        <p>
            In 1992 this Coordination was created with the purpose of incorporing Information Technologies 
            and communicactions among the different processes of this Autonomous University of Queretaro 
            and to take advantage of them for the development of the funcion of this University.
        </p>
        <p>
            The main goal of this Coordination is focused in supporting the activities of the University, establishing
            communication systems, access to information and computing resources available to all dependencies of the 
            University through the development and management of Informatization Services and the Institutional Computing 
            Network. 
        </p>
        <p>
            Among the activities we carry out to achieve our role as Informatization are the following:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To plan the development and implementation of the Institutional Computing Network.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To integrate universitary dependencies to aforementioned Network.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To coordinate application management together with the people in charge of Computing Centre in order 
                    to achieve a better use of network resources. 
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To implement methods and policies needed for Network and Services operation, management and security.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To bring up University's external interconection strategies to Internet and Internet II. 
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To incorporate new Information Technologies for Network development.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To develop a platform which works as a gateway between computing management systems.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To establish appropiate mecanisms to attend and solve problems and flaws presented in Network and services.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To provide an Informatization Services Wallet.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To provide technical support and consultancy to universitary staff's requests related to the department.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    to Analize and implement new services.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    To outline different training programs directed towards skill development in software management tools.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
